Words cannot express how proud I am of every 👏single 👏person 👏 in this photo.  Each of them artist; together the best damn photo team in the business! I literally could not do this without them. 

This was suppose to be @lollapalooza #9 for me, 4th steering the photo ship. But…the day before leaving, I had a lil bike wreck & fractured my femur & collar bone, both on my left side 🙌

After a few screws in my leg, a few days in the hospital & almost 10 days of bed/couch rest, I’m starting to see the silver linings:

1) SO SO SO thankful to have such an amazing & handsome human by my side for this 😭 Our definition of together is being rewritten & I’m even more excited about our next chapter. I love you @tadunson ❤️ You are the best medicine I can ask for. 

2. I love what I do so much & am so proud of the business @grant.pal & I have built; but more importantly the family that’s been created. ❤️❤️

A thank you beyond words to @grant.pal & @haylee.kee for taking over & making this papa so proud ♥️😭♥️ 

3. A forced slow down after a life always going about 10 over…not a bad thing, at all. Time to work on some new creative endeavors…

4. I haven’t been outside for longer than 30min in the past 10 days!! It’s 107 outside 🔥 🙏

My dad summed it up perfectly…

These next few months will be but a speck in your life.

Thank you to everyone who has reached out and stopped by 🙏 ❤️
